de.hshl.obj.data

Class Late<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hshl.obj.data.Late<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the cached value

    public final class Late<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Lazily instantiates a value once, using the specified constructor. Simplifies caching a value, and thus can be used to simplify creating singletons. This class is thread-safe.
    Author:
    Johannes Vollmer
